<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cater-vi">cater <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'keɪtə(r)/    美 /'keɪtər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>承办宴席；满足需求；迎合：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>cater for</strong> weddings. 
我们承办婚宴。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Children are well <strong>catered for</strong> with apple-themed games.
苹果主题的游戏让孩子们感到非常满足。</p><footer>2016 全国改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The university started some new language programs to cater<strong><em>_</em></strong> the country’s Silk Road Economic Belt.<br />
  （2015 江苏改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. for  </p></div>